abiDocs.name: executeProposal
abiDocs.notice: Finish vote     * Count the votes proposal #`proposalID` and execute it if approved

inputs.name: supportsProposal
inputs.description: either in favor or against it

abiDocs.name: vote
abiDocs.notice: Log a vote for a proposal     * Vote `supportsProposal? in support of : against` proposal #`proposalID`

inputs.name: beneficiary
inputs.description: who to send the ether to

inputs.name: weiAmount
inputs.description: amount of ether to send, in wei

abiDocs.name: newProposal
abiDocs.notice: Add Proposal     * Propose to send `weiAmount / 1e18` ether to `beneficiary` for `jobDescription`. `transactionBytecode ? Contains : Does not contain` code.

inputs.name: minimumSharesToPassAVote
inputs.description: proposal can vote only if the sum of shares held by all voters exceed this number

inputs.name: minSecondsForDebate
inputs.description: the minimum amount of delay between when a proposal is made and when it can be executed

abiDocs.name: changeVotingRules
abiDocs.notice: Change voting rules     * Make so that proposals need to be discussed for at least `minSecondsForDebate` seconds and all voters combined must own more than `minimumSharesToPassAVote` shares of token `sharesAddress` to be executed

inputs.name: newOwner
inputs.description: The address to transfer ownership to.

abiDocs.name: transferOwnership
abiDocs.details: Allows the current owner to transfer control of the contract to a newOwner.
